# <type>(<scope>): <subject>
#
# <body>
#
# <footer>
#
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Types (必选):
#   feat:     新功能 (A new feature)
#   fix:      修复Bug (A bug fix)
#   docs:     文档变更 (Documentation only changes)
#   style:    代码格式 (Formatting, missing semi colons, etc)
#   refactor: 重构 (A code change that neither fixes a bug nor adds a feature)
#   perf:     性能优化 (A code change that improves performance)
#   test:     测试 (Adding missing tests)
#   build:    构建系统 (Changes to build system or dependencies)
#   ci:       CI配置 (Changes to CI configuration files and scripts)
#   chore:    杂项 (Other changes that don't modify src or test files)
#   revert:   回滚 (Reverts a previous commit)
#
# Scope (可选):
#   decoder, registration, libraw, build, docs, tests, etc.
#
# Subject (必选):
#   - 使用祈使句，小写，不加句号
#   - 不超过50个字符
#
# Body (可选):
#   - 解释"是什么"和"为什么"，而不是"怎么做"
#   - 每行不超过72个字符
#
# Footer (可选):
#   - Breaking changes: BREAKING CHANGE: <description>
#   - Issue references: Closes #123, Fixes #456
#
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 示例:
#
# feat(decoder): add RW2 thumbnail extraction
#
# Implement IWICBitmapDecoder::GetThumbnail() to extract
# embedded JPEG thumbnails from RW2 EXIF data, improving
# preview speed by 80%.
#
# Closes #15
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
